Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
view_package_results(25.10)                        view_package_results(25.10)

Name
       view_package_results

Syntax
       view_package_results

       [-help]

       [-result_file <<filename>>]

       -type <<package_analysis_type>>

       [-workspace <<workspacename>>]

       Specifies  to  view the package IR drop analysis results in the PowerDC
       GUI which will be invoked from within Voltus/Innovus.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs the command usage and a brief description about the com-
              mand parameters.

       -result_file <<filename>>
              Specifies the name of the .xml result file.

       -type <<package_analysis_type>>
              Specifies the type of package analysis. Currently, the  software
              supports only the dc package analysis type.

       -workspace <<workspace_name>>
              Specifies the workspace name for package analysis (powerDC). The
              file name extension is .pdcx.

Example
              * The  following  example specifies to view the package analysis
                results

                view_package_results -type dc

Related Information
              * set_advanced_package_options

              * extract_package

              * "Package Analysis" in the Voltus IC Power  Integrity  Solution
                User Guide

